---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PRUVIQ - Don't Believe. Verify.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="min-h-[90vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4 tracking-wider">CRYPTO STRATEGY SIMULATION</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          Don't Believe.<br/>
          <span class="text-[--color-accent]">Verify.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[--color-text-muted] mb-2 font-mono">
          Every strategy tested. Every result published.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[--color-text-muted] mb-8 max-w-2xl">
          Simulate trading strategies on 500+ coins with 2+ years of data.
          Realistic fees, slippage, and drawdowns. No cherry-picking. Free forever.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="/strategies"
             class="bg-[--color-accent] text-[--color-bg] px-8 py-3 rounded font-semibold text-center hover:bg-[--color-accent-dim] transition-colors">
            Explore Strategies &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="/blog"
             class="border border-[--color-border] text-[--color-text] px-8 py-3 rounded font-semibold text-center hover:border-[--color-accent] hover:text-[--color-accent] transition-colors">
            Raise Your Trading IQ
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded p-4 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
            <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-2xl font-bold">500+</p>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">Coins Simulated</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded p-4 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
            <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-2xl font-bold">2+ yrs</p>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">Historical Data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded p-4 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
            <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold">100%</p>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">Free &amp; Transparent</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section id="the-problem" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">THE PROBLEM</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Crypto Trading is Broken.</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-3xl font-bold mb-3">$154B+</p>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Liquidated in 2025</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Flash crashes wiped out retail leverage traders.
            Most bots were optimized for bull runs that ended years ago.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-3xl font-bold mb-3">2,000%</p>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Backtest Fantasies</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            That "guaranteed return"? Probably overfitted on 6 months of cherry-picked data.
            Live results? Nowhere to be found.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-3xl font-bold mb-3">47/day</p>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Signal Spam</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Telegram groups spam "URGENT BUY" alerts all day.
            No accountability. No track record. No proof.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg">
          You don't need more signals. You need
          <strong class="text-[--color-accent]">one system that proves itself.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE ANSWER -->
  <section id="approach" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">THE ANSWER</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Prove Everything. Hide Nothing.</h2>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">
        PRUVIQ lets you test crypto strategies before risking real money.
        Every simulation uses realistic costs, and every result &mdash; including failures &mdash; is published.
        Not a signal service. A verification tool.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">01</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Backtest Before You Trade</h3>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
                Every strategy is tested on 500+ coins across 2+ years of data
                before risking real capital. No exceptions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">02</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Simulate Before You Trade</h3>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
                Test any strategy on historical data with real fees and slippage.
                See the drawdowns, the losing streaks, the actual risk. Then decide.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">03</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Kill What Doesn't Work</h3>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
                We've already killed 3 strategies that lost money in simulation.
                No ego. If the data says stop, we stop.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">04</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Evolve With the Market</h3>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
                Markets change. Strategies must change too.
                PRUVIQ continuously tests, validates, and adapts.
                What runs today may be different tomorrow &mdash; and that's the point.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">THE $14,000 LESSON</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In early 2026, we built a "momentum breakout" strategy that backtested at +400%.
            It lost <strong class="text-[--color-red]">$14,115</strong> in simulation.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Why? Look-ahead bias. Overfitting. Ignoring market regime.
            Every classic mistake in the book.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            That failure taught us more than any winning streak.
            We rebuilt from scratch with one rule:
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono font-bold">
            "If you can't prove it survives, don't trade it."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EVIDENCE -->
  <section id="evidence" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">EVIDENCE</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Verified, Not Promised.</h2>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">
        We don't show you best-case scenarios. We show you everything.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
        <!-- What we show -->
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">WHAT WE PUBLISH</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Every trade entry & exit with timestamps</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Win rate, loss rate, and net P&L</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Strategy changes and the data behind each decision</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Failed experiments and why they were killed</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Risk parameters and position sizing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What we don't promise -->
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-sm mb-4">WHAT WE DON'T PROMISE</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Guaranteed returns (no one can)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>"Get rich quick" with leverage</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Secret proprietary "AI" magic</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Cherry-picked backtest results</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Permanent strategies that never change</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">HOW SIMULATIONS WORK</h3>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 font-mono text-sm">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Coins</span>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">500+</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Data</span>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">2+ Years</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Fees</span>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">Included</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Slippage</span>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">Modeled</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-4">
          Our open-source engine simulates strategies with realistic costs.
          No look-ahead bias. Results you can trust and replicate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="system" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">THE SYSTEM</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Code, Not Gut Feeling.</h2>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">
        No guessing. No cherry-picking. An open-source Python engine
        that simulates strategies with realistic market conditions.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">SELECT</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Pick a strategy from our library. BB Squeeze, momentum,
            mean reversion &mdash; or bring your own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">SIMULATE</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Run it on 500+ coins with 2+ years of data.
            Fees, slippage, and drawdowns included. No shortcuts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">VERIFY</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            See the full picture: win rate, max drawdown,
            losing streaks, and profit factor. Then decide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">OPEN SOURCE ENGINE</h3>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-sm">
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Engine</span>
            <span>Python + Pandas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Data</span>
            <span>ccxt (Multi-Exchange)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Storage</span>
            <span>Parquet</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Bias Prevention</span>
            <span>5 QA Tests</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Cost Model</span>
            <span>Fees + Slippage</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Community</span>
            <span>Telegram</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE BUILDER -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">THE BUILDER</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">One Developer. Zero Excuses.</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed mb-6">
            PRUVIQ is built and operated by <strong class="text-[--color-text]">JPLee</strong> &mdash;
            a developer who got tired of crypto projects that promise everything and prove nothing.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed mb-6">
            No team. No investors. No exit strategy. Just one person building simulation tools
            with AI, testing strategies on years of data, and publishing every result &mdash; including failures.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed mb-6">
            If a strategy fails in simulation, you'll see it fail. If it works, you'll see the data.
            <strong class="text-[--color-accent]">That's the deal.</strong>
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm">PRINCIPLES</h3>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Evidence over hype. Always.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Show losses. Transparency builds trust.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Kill strategies that don't perform. No ego.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Risk management is not optional.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">STRATEGY GRAVEYARD</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mb-4">Strategies we tested and killed based on evidence.</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
            <div class="border-b border-[--color-border] pb-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                <span class="font-mono">Momentum LONG</span>
                <span class="text-[--color-red] font-mono">-$14,115</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs">37.5% win rate. Needed 71.4% to break even. Killed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-b border-[--color-border] pb-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                <span class="font-mono">BB Squeeze LONG</span>
                <span class="text-[--color-red] font-mono">-$26</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs">51% win rate. Negative expected value. Killed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-b border-[--color-border] pb-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                <span class="font-mono">HV Squeeze</span>
                <span class="text-[--color-text-muted] font-mono">Inconclusive</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs">Insufficient edge vs BB Squeeze. Abandoned.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                <span class="font-mono">ATR Breakout</span>
                <span class="text-[--color-text-muted] font-mono">Inconclusive</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs">Tested, didn't outperform. Shelved.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/graveyard" class="inline-block text-[--color-accent] text-xs mt-4 font-mono hover:underline">
            See full autopsy reports &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAVE ON FEES -->
  <section id="fees" class="py-20 border-t border-[--color-border]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">SAVE ON FEES</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Stop Paying Full Price to Trade.</h2>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">
        Fees hit every trade. We compared 9 exchanges so you don't have to.
        Sign up through PRUVIQ and get discounted rates &mdash; on any exchange.
      </p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">Binance</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-xl font-bold">20% off</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Largest volume globally</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">Bybit</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-xl font-bold">20% off</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Lifetime discount</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">OKX</p>
