      </div>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] mb-8">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">HOW MUCH DO FEES ACTUALLY COST?</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div>
            <p class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-2xl font-bold">$1,200</p>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm mt-1">Annual fees at $100K/mo (standard)</p>
